                    <button class="fw-mb-15 fw-border-style-solid fw-border-width-2 fw-border-radius-3 fw-bg-color-white fw-border-color-gray fw-width-1-1 fw-block fw-fz-16 fw-pt-12 fw-pb-12 fw-color-purple">Продублировать письмо</button>
                    <button class="fw-border-style-solid fw-border-width-2 fw-border-radius-3 fw-bg-color-white fw-border-color-gray fw-width-1-1 fw-block fw-fz-16 fw-pt-12 fw-pb-12 fw-color-purple">Указать другой email</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </form>
{% endblock %}



